        <h1 class="heading-color text-center" id="title">The Future of Web Design in 2025: Latest Trends</h1>       
         <p class="pill-purple text-center mt-4"><a class="text-decoration-none text-white" href="https://brandstory.in/contact-us/">Contact Us</a></p>
         <img class="d-none" id="image" src="https://brandstory.in/blogs/assets/images/future-webdesign/banner.jpg" alt="">
